           <h1 class="article-header__title" lang="en">Facile Syntheses of N-Heterocyclic Carbene Precursors through I<sub>2</sub>- or NIS-Promoted Amidiniumation of <em>N</em>-Alkenyl Formamidines</h1>
           <div class="article-header__authors-container">
            <h2 class="is-accessible">Authors</h2>
